sequenceDiagram
autonumber
participant User
participant Frontend
participant API
participant DB

User->>Frontend: View room details
Frontend->>API: GET /api/rooms/:roomId
API->>API: parsePositiveInt(roomId)
alt Invalid room id
API-->>Frontend: 400 Invalid room id
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Valid room id
API->>DB: Query room by id
alt Room not found
DB-->>API: empty
API-->>Frontend: 404 Room not found
Frontend-->>User: Show not found
else Found
DB-->>API: row
API-->>Frontend: 200 room details
Frontend-->>User: Render room
end
end
